{"tid":1236081,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"岩岩發夢夢到呢個人（你講我畫）","createTime":"2019-06-17T10:40:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T10:46:22.000Z","uid":208927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cc63857d7bce25cbeb237b3a9aa098ac29850a63","tid":1236081,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:40:20.000Z","msg":"（幫大家減減壓，成個禮拜都有好多負能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n（如有雷同純屬巧合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所有關於個角色係夢境入面㗎，<br />\n唔好噤認真）<br />\n我岩岩發惡夢<br />\n夢見我同朋友仔過海返九龍去左間餐館到<br />\n有個大媽負責落單同抹枱<br />\n噤岩電影播緊新聞<br />\n佢見到啲內容開始係到自己講野<br />\n仲大大聲噤方死我地聽唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟著指住我地個方向講<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3XmzU8k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3XmzU8k.png&h=4138cd0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我嬲到火屎都煲滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嬲醒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我等陣又返去瞓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家可唔可以比啲意見我發夢可以點對付佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4722abc49f532d2e446e586ee1dd9de852c8fa9","tid":1236081,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:41:25.000Z","msg":"電視*"},{"pid":"4de409482af6271e29c87aa48b66439bc00a05f9","tid":1236081,"uid":44289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:43:56.000Z","msg":"通常呢啲食肆都好污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又曱甴又老鼠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋消失又有啲問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087f34edef1d0cbf3422c1e65550acd597a13db7","tid":1236081,"uid":44289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:44:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常呢啲食肆都好